193
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:02,800
Rong Yin, I need to bathe.

194
00:12:19,400 --> 00:12:20,320
Stay back!

195
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:23,360
Don't come over!

196
00:12:33,160 --> 00:12:34,680
- You have a face
- Let me go.

197
00:12:34,830 --> 00:12:37,760
- even more beautiful than an actress.
- Please let me go.

198
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:46,520
You even smell nice.

199
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:19,720
I didn't expect

200
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:22,520
to reach this move so soon.

201
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:24,720
This moment...

202
00:13:26,520 --> 00:13:28,440
I don't want to wait anymore.

203
00:13:39,380 --> 00:13:41,760
♪Like a drowning whale♪

204
00:13:42,980 --> 00:13:45,120
♪Falling into you♪

205
00:13:46,910 --> 00:13:49,200
♪Into every inch of your body♪

206
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:52,310
♪Then it fell apart♪

207
00:13:52,750 --> 00:13:54,690
♪Without a trace♪

208
00:13:54,690 --> 00:13:56,800
♪Like a warm winter♪

209
00:13:57,520 --> 00:13:59,470
♪Running barefoot to you♪

210
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:04,430
♪Spreading in your cold palm♪

211
00:14:04,750 --> 00:14:07,310
♪Vanishing in your warm breath♪

212
00:14:07,310 --> 00:14:10,410
♪Because nobody knows♪

213
00:14:10,760 --> 00:14:13,670
♪Can't ever go back♪

214
00:14:14,360 --> 00:14:17,710
♪You touch my heart, my heart♪

215
00:14:18,010 --> 00:14:21,050
♪Why is it so calm?♪

216
00:14:21,540 --> 00:14:24,530
♪Cause everybody knows♪

217
00:14:25,110 --> 00:14:28,060
♪Can't ever go back♪

218
